FuncDef: This command specifies theprefix-stringassociated with theexport-override.

ParaDef.Info: Up to an 8 character string. If the 8 character prefix is "ABCDEFG_" for a particular node, the cflowd export override would generate IPv4 interface names such as ABCDEFG_255.255.255.255 or IPv6 as ABCDEFG_2001:DB8:EF01:2345::/64. By default the prefix will be left blank.
